   Top Ten Initial Focus Items
   Affecting the Citys Visual Image
     * Unsightly property condition
     * Neighborhood Eyesores
     * Litter
     * Uncontainerized waste / Piles of rubbish
     * Illegal dumping
     * Waste disposal practices
     * Graffiti on public and private locations
     * Illegal posters on trees and utility poles
     * Abandoned vehicles
     * Education and enforcement
